definition: to hit (the mark)/to be hit by/to suffer/to win (a prize, a lottery)
will/shall/to use/to take/to checkmate/just a short while ago/(introduces object of main verb, used in the same way as 把[ba3])

sentences.english: Melt the butter in a small saucepan.
sentences.chinese: 在小汤锅中将黄油融化。

sentences.english: Jones will be missing from the team line-up.
sentences.chinese: 球队阵容中将没有琼斯。

sentences.english: The deck spits out a two-seven offsuit come playoff time.
sentences.chinese: 现在队伍中将会有两个七尺大个出现在季后赛了。

sentences.english: Octopus oracle Paul is predicting Germany will be defeated by Spain at the World Cup semifinal.
sentences.chinese: 八爪鱼保罗推测德国在半决赛中将被西班牙战胜。

sentences.english: Some of the cells in the resultant mouse will contain the inactivated gene.
sentences.chinese: 最终老鼠的某些细胞中将含有灭活基因。

sentences.english: Though thou shouldst bray a fool in the mortar, as when a pestle striketh upon sodden barley, his folly would not be taken from him.
sentences.chinese: 你尽可在臼中将愚人舂碎，但他的昏愚却永不能铲除。

sentences.english: What will the process of evolution create?
sentences.chinese: 进化的过程中将会产生哪些变化？

sentences.english: An example of acceptance test report is presented in the next sections.
sentences.chinese: 在以下章节中将会给出验收测试报告的例子。

sentences.english: The film will decide the Palmed'Or Award.
sentences.chinese: 影片中将评出金棕榈奖。

sentences.english: In his speech, he compared the plight of gays to that of blacks during the civil-rights era.
sentences.chinese: 他在演讲中将同志的境遇比作民权运动时期的黑人。

sentences.english: Combine powdered sugar and 2 tablespoons lemon juice in small bowl.
sentences.chinese: 在一小碗中将糖粉及2汤匙柠檬汁混匀。

sentences.english: If a competitor holsters a firearm during the course of fire, the following will apply.
sentences.chinese: 如果选手在比赛中将枪枝收回枪套，应适用下列条件。

sentences.english: True, there will be patch es of perkiness in the emerging world.
sentences.chinese: 而事实表明，新兴国家集团中将会出现新的活力。

sentences.english: What tendency will be shown in the reproduction of medical disputes?
sentences.chinese: 在再现医疗纠纷的过程中将表现出怎样的媒介倾向。

sentences.english: The bottom right window contains our action items.
sentences.chinese: 右下方的窗口中将包括操作项。

sentences.english: We retrieve information about the user that will be useful in later requests.
sentences.chinese: 我们检索在后来的请求中将会有用的关于用户的信息。
